author: Master_Wu
title: Not a big fan
review:
To me, Gimli is not that special of a Lego minifigure. So, attaching him to a keychain wasn't very sensational.

I know this is kind of late because this was released a long time ago. But if anyone is still trying to get them, I would recommend some other keychains first. This guy is okay, he's just not as cool looking as some of the other characters.
